dullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the Muslim is directed in the right manner to achieve the level of one who regularly fasts and stands for prayer with the verses of Allah, due to his good character and his generous\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28982,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/09\/qunut-juhd-al-muqil\/","url_meta":{"origin":40145,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Virtues: Which prayer, charity, and faith is best?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Umayr ibn Qatadah reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, which prayer is best?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOne finished with a long supplication.\u201d The man said, \u201cWhich charity is best?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cGreat effort with little means.\u201d The man said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":649,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/03\/23\/faith-is-perfected-character\/","url_meta":{"origin":40145,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Character: Best believers are kind to family","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 23, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\u201cVerily, the most complete of believers in faith are those with the